Just to add (for English users), I needed to change the user id in the .reg file to the one in my windows (XP) instance
(The long number in: "HKEY_USERS\S-1-5-21-484763869-1957994488-1343024091-1003" of the "cooledit.reg" file needs to be changed ot the unique number used in each instance of windows before the file is ran and the contents added to the registry)
